df['Model_Reg2'] = coef['Intercept'] + (coef['Benzen']*df['Benzen']) +(coef['Propylen']*df['Propylen']) +(coef['OxoplastO']*df['OxoplastO'])+(coef['Szlaka_tytanowa']*df['Szlaka_tytanowa'])+(coef['Poliamid']*df['Poliamid'])
df['Model_Reg2']= np.round(df['Model_Reg2'], decimals=0)
